        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued September 8 at 6:08PM CDT until September 8 at 6:45PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 607 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 6 miles southeast of
Elmwood, or 18 miles south of Beaver, moving east at 20 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible. Hail
damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Booker and Darrouzett.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
